snippet.title: SLEEP AWAKE
snippet.description:
SLEEP AWAKE is a first-person psychedelic horror game set in the far future.

The debut title from EYES OUT will be among the first titles released by publisher Blumhouse Games.  

Visit eyes-out.com for more info, follow us on socials, and join the mailing list. 👁️
